lead_paragraph: Bradley Wright-Phillips volleyed home Connor Lade's cross in the 90th minute to give the New York Red Bulls a 2-2 tie with the Chicago Fire on Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: Wright-Phillips Scores Late, Red Bulls Tie Fire 2-2
